reviews.review:
It is a game where the sequence surpasses the first game. Portal 2 is way more fun! This game is mandatory, everyone should play it once in their lives. Worth it!

Pros:
- Great graphics;
- Excellent soundtrack;
- Interesting plot with great characters;
- Challenging puzzles;
- Amazing cooperative mode;

Cons:
- Very addictive;
- Occasional dizziness (depending on you gameplay);
